{"tid":2370781,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一拳與磚陣 - 陳也","createTime":"2021-01-18T09:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T09:42:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1bc7722e9412706123c2b835274f6e152b1125ac","tid":2370781,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:24:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210118/ZQPXZMZSV5AVXMAECZMIP4YP5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210118%2FZQPXZMZSV5AVXMAECZMIP4YP5Q%2F&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS0YnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=ebba1a06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210118%2FZQPXZMZSV5AVXMAECZMIP4YP5Q%2F&h=8a5641ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210118/ZQPXZMZSV5AVXMAECZMIP4YP5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n一拳與磚陣 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KD8zpAM1i7Fls4cpbKJ1l8AMZ3Q=/5472x3648/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TCRQK6DK5RFPHNJSOJWHXWX6KU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKD8zpAM1i7Fls4cpbKJ1l8AMZ3Q%3D%2F5472x3648%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTCRQK6DK5RFPHNJSOJWHXWX6KU.JPG&h=694821dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一拳書館開班教人寫信給在囚手足，兼導賞本地與外國監獄文學作品。<br />\n<br />\n這種港版「聯乘活動」全世界罕見！這一年只有少部份香港人能夠賺盡猛灌的北水，司法機關與普通人一樣，要頂住瘟疫扭轉頸脖面北，審時度勢，迴避紅線。寒風凜凜，香港人凍僵的不止手腳。冷風逆行中的我們，握緊拳頭，向在囚手足寫什麼好呢？<br />\n<br />\n記得去年十月底到港大學生會睇過反送中「物鈙展」，裏面15件展品中，黃廠口罩已被打沉，蘋果日報遭武警殺入堆填區大搜捕，肥佬黎腰纏鐵鏈又再從蝴蝶谷押往赤柱。展品中的三張保釋紙的主人，已經走出黑隧，投奔自由了嗎？抑或像展品之一的岳少年那張獄中書信所說的，「有位手足刑滿出冊了」。寫信後的半年，岳少年也在上個月刑滿獲釋。但有更多的香港人還押在牢，出入冊的逆差明顯。沒控罪在身的也憂慮清晨六點響起的門鐘。寫給獄中手足的書信，很可能是「探路Q&amp;A」，絕望中緊抓「牢獄適應指南」，摸着手足的石頭過河&hellip;&hellip;噢，磚頭才對。<span class=\"orange\">重看各區Brick Arches的新聞照片，手足的設計，靚過水馬好很好很多！</span>高牆內屈指抱拳計算，塌下來的磚，能佈出多少磚陣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6850609696262603e0327e1eea093600fbbadbe2","tid":2370781,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T09:42:12.000Z","msg":"up"}]}